000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>近年? 08年咋嘛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n轉眼都過左快10年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老了我的偶像<br />\n但講真佢控球,腳下功夫以世界最頂尖既球星來講其實好一般<br />\n不過佢全盛期既速度足以彌補晒呢個缺點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係撚 明明佢控球同腳下功夫都係頂級 明明呢兩樣佢同世界最頂尖比都唔會輸蝕只係你睇精華見到佢多爆人姐 佢<span style=\"color: red;\">視野 分波</span> 控球都係一絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪撚剩係睇精華啦 明明卡卡都勁撚有創造力 比波靚  個個睇精華就唔撚識 佢最勁仲有20-30碼既燙射 準到癲</blockquote><br />\n咪係,卡卡點會控球一般</blockquote><br />\n佢係太過實而不華<br />\n令人感覺求鳩其腳內檔控咁<br />\n但假假地叫控到個波先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然卡卡係勁 但呢兩樣一定唔係頂級<br />\n佢啲分波最常都係引走左好大個空位再比隊 其實只要踢波識用腦既都識比<br />\n簡易啲講 你睇電視果陣係明顯地睇得出佢會咁比"},{"pid":"6e1aa27189805228342ddcf5e25496c7a60bafb8","tid":396054,"uid":34490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:54:18.000Z","msg":"顛峰期短左少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88984ee9d4d81a5f26ea1439e04b8deb9961224d","tid":396054,"uid":34490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:54:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>吾系掛<br />\nCaptain marvellous 勁巧多<br />\n系衰在仆左一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCaptain Marvellous 係邊鳩個？<br />\nCaptain fabulous呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8828c2ce1e634997f56bcf18b07ce98a58a5c414","tid":396054,"uid":17392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:59:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賣金嗓子就叻</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1eb617d71076a0a74743d7ba7048a06a454de3d","tid":396054,"uid":34490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT